Oh, and don't get me started on wizards... If you have a VoQed Wizard, with a bard in group... Its insane. <br>
<br>
Mages with Charm can get 550 DPS pets. pet+paltank+rouge= 30k mob dead in 25sec. That gives us druids a reason to light the fire and get working pulling.<br>
<br>
Classes in PoP zones are pretty balanced. with a few AA a druid can MGB a 250 a tic heal that lasts 45sec w/o useing mana. can use 5.5k &quot;mini&quot;CHs, can nuke about half as effectively as a wizard. oh, and use a 650 DS every 3min for that &quot;viola&quot; effect. If i feel sorry for anyone it has to be poor poor Bards, no... Beastlords.. not really.. Clerics, ha. Druids, oh poor pitiful me. enchanters, being a hastewhore sucks, but hey, your vital!. ... Shaman, I love going from oom to FM in less than a minute. Warrior, can tank PoP named! Wizard, BOOM!<br>
<br>
They did a good job on class balanceing. Healer+Tank+Slower and 3 others= a group. A lot better than needing Cleric, Shaman, Ench/bard, Pal, and DPS, DPS. <br>
<br>
